</tbody>
</table>
</figure>
<p data-index="2089"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="12-27" id="Page_12-27" data-index="2090"></span>Book value of $16,250 is greater than net cash flows of $13,000. Therefore, the license is impaired. The impairment loss is computed as follows.</p>
