<p id="c12-ex-0073" data-index="2765"><b data-index="2766">c.</b> In 2020, Winston determined that a competitor's product would make the New Age Piano obsolete and the patent worthless by December 31, 2021. Prepare all journal entries required in 2020 and 2021.</p>
</blockquote>
